messages.text: The people elected Donald Trump to be President - not Elon Musk. Having an unelected billionaire, with his own foreign debts and motives, raiding US classified information is a grave threat to national security. This should not be a partisan issue.
I say disrespected but what are you guys doing? Why are you not trying to stop them? Why is there not impeachment papers on the table and someone arresting Musk.
